Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.53,0:02:45.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高举圣剑的英雄……
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.58,0:02:47.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是导师的壁画！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.49,0:03:11.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,导师的传说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.76,0:03:19.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「那里是天之都 是遥远山峰上的圣域」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.06,0:03:26.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「都城之门紧闭 只有统治人世者可以开启」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.91,0:03:30.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「导师带领天族 降临至大地」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.41,0:03:37.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「导师携天族之力 驱散灾祸之暗 拯救世界」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.50,0:03:42.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只是个传说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.00,0:03:45.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界已经……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.11,0:05:02.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是……？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.17,0:05:41.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.19,0:06:08.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是阿斯嘉德时代的遗物吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.34,0:06:35.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.99,0:06:40.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,导师的纹章
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.09,0:06:45.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神圣的印记所照亮的场所……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.96,0:07:30.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,道路因导师的纹章而开启
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.50,0:07:33.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传说居然是真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.94,0:08:26.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.13,0:08:29.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里竟然有这样的遗迹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:30.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.82,0:08:33.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米库里欧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.01,0:08:37.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 你又一个人跑来这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.17,0:08:40.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是个普通的人类 得多小心一些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.11,0:08:42.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掉下去就不得了了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.01,0:08:48.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 也亏了你这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.75,0:08:54.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棒极了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.38,0:08:57.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.81,0:09:04.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我不认为爷爷他们不知道这个遗迹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.23,0:09:07.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.31,0:09:12.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都知道我们对遗迹探险有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.16,0:09:14.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说……
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.16,0:09:17.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.37,0:09:20.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了 就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.97,0:09:25.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你找到了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.28,0:09:27.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就看着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.20,0:09:38.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此 是爷爷的幻术啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.23,0:09:41.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还真能注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.36,0:09:44.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.16,0:09:47.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是要去探险咯！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.80,0:09:48.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.30,0:09:51.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.15,0:09:53.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.46,0:09:58.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是很久以前被封印的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.39,0:10:00.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不允许你们再靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.49,0:10:05.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能去探险 也不能调查 懂了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.39,0:10:19.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么爷爷不想让我们进那个遗迹呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.93,0:10:23.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我翻到了 米库里欧 「降临之章」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.23,0:10:28.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「在遥远的神代时代 当黑暗在世间蔓延时」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.23,0:10:31.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「其人自天降临于世 取回光明」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.59,0:10:38.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「天族居于世间各处 支撑万物」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.82,0:10:41.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「其中便有这天之都」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.56,0:10:47.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是认为白天我们看到的遗迹就是天之都吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.43,0:10:48.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.93,0:10:55.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「天之都的人们开始参拜」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.45,0:10:59.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「其中有资质的人能够同天族进行对话」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.41,0:11:01.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类和天族……
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.58,0:11:07.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「天族给予人类恩惠 人类向天族奉上祈祷」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.98,0:11:15.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「有资质的人作为中间的桥梁 天之都最终成为人类与天族交流之地」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.12,0:11:19.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.10,0:11:24.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,《天遗见闻录》
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.25,0:11:27.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是很喜欢这本书啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.84,0:11:28.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那当然了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.17,0:11:32.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从这本天遗见闻录上记述的特征来看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.07,0:11:36.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得那个遗迹是天之都的可能性很高
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.00,0:11:38.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是要去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.41,0:11:40.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.08,0:11:44.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那当然……而且我还有一件事比较在意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.75,0:11:51.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没注意到吗？ 那个遗迹不在爷爷的加护领域之内
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.72,0:11:53.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么一说还真是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.47,0:11:55.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是得去调查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.56,0:11:59.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样好吗？不听爷爷的嘱咐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.77,0:12:01.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你不去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.32,0:12:07.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁能更快发现厉害的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.76,0:12:08.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咱们就来比比看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.34,0:12:10.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.30,0:13:58.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.80,0:14:07.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高举圣剑的英雄 这是导师的壁画！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.81,0:14:10.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒……
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.76,0:14:18.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.51,0:14:21.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,导师的纹章
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.01,0:14:27.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛干嘛 米库里欧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.17,0:14:30.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次被你抢先了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.87,0:14:32.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不止是这次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.13,0:14:34.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.02,0:14:46.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这雷电……并不是自然气象
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.78,0:15:07.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禅雷大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.41,0:15:11.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯姆吗 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.73,0:15:16.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在我的领域之外作乱是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.57,0:15:19.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 要如何处理？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.88,0:15:23.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷和米库里欧还没回来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.44,0:15:23.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.79,0:15:30.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这俩孩子真让人头疼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.47,0:15:36.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说是被前人留下的未曾见过的遗物所吸引……
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.44,0:15:40.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯姆 现在先不作行动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.02,0:15:41.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.96,0:15:53.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是神殿吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.27,0:16:04.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走到头了……
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.53,0:16:39.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果走进我的领域 不会轻饶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.41,0:16:44.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来像是这个遗迹在呼唤雷电啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.60,0:16:52.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.41,0:16:59.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点离开这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.22,0:17:23.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,释放双流！ Twin Flow！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.07,0:17:28.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.10,0:17:33.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.61,0:17:35.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼……
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.23,0:17:38.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才真危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.99,0:17:44.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到地下也有遗迹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.68,0:17:46.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掉下来还挺值的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.31,0:17:51.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 还是先找回去的路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.34,0:17:53.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.96,0:18:00.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 真高！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.62,0:18:02.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才也够高的了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.77,0:18:05.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里有壁画 就不值得在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.62,0:18:07.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.88,0:18:11.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在那儿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.18,0:18:13.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这种地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.33,0:18:16.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那啥 米库里欧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.66,0:18:21.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是个人类
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.05,0:18:24.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类？ 为什么会在这种地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.14,0:18:25.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咱们得过去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.47,0:18:31.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷不是说过吗？别和人类扯上关系
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.43,0:18:34.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能放着不管啊！她说不定还活着呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.56,0:18:40.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道啦 我也来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.82,0:18:41.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米库里欧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.20,0:18:44.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是要怎么到那边去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.50,0:18:53.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你……
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.16,0:18:55.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这个难道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.16,0:18:58.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走喽！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.84,0:19:07.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么人呐！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.58,0:19:09.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你下到这里 也过不……
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.52,0:19:12.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米库里欧 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.10,0:19:19.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.36,0:19:28.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你居然能注意到这里有透明的桥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.36,0:19:35.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.70,0:19:36.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.41,0:19:40.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这桥是怎么做出来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.59,0:19:43.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靠人类的技术肯定是做不出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.39,0:19:48.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说至少是神话时代的古旧产物了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.25,0:19:50.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.67,0:20:04.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是重新考虑一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.27,0:20:06.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.69,0:20:10.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个……你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.01,0:20:19.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.22,0:20:25.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得……是被落雷……
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.67,0:20:32.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 看起来没事 站得起来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.69,0:20:43.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 似乎让你担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.14,0:20:45.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.75,0:20:49.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是史雷 请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.86,0:20:50.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷……
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.13,0:20:57.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷……
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.36,0:21:00.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是导师吗？
